   During inclement weather, or state emergencies, please see the Department of Administrative Services Building Closure Notices for State OfficesAll DMV offices, including DMV Headquarters and the Business Regulation office in Salem, will be closed on the dates listed below due to holidays. 

Note: Please see the 
      Web page for your target DMV office for unscheduled office closures.2024 ClosuresState agencies will be closed on the following days in 2024:New Years Day observed - Monday, Jan. 1, 2024Martin Luther King Jr. Day - Monday, Jan. 15, 2024President's Day - Monday, Feb. 19, 2024Memorial Day - Monday, May 27, 2024Juneteenth - Wednesday, June 19, 2024Independence Day - Thursday, July 4, 2024Labor Day - Monday, Sept. 2, 2024Veterans Day observed - Monday, Nov. 11, 2024Thanksgiving Day - Thursday, Nov. 28, 2024Day after Thanksgiving - Friday, Nov. 29, 2024Christmas Day - Wednesday, Dec. 25, 2024




























































